name: Access Staffing
overview: Access Staffing and Access Technical Staffing (www.accesstechnical.com), founded in 1998, provide expertise in the search, recruitment and placement of Information Technology and Information Systems professionals, primarily for direct hire by your firm. We deal with both technical specialists and managers in the Information Technology field, including programmers, analysts, software engineers, web developers and designers, database and system administrators, and network specialists, as well as all levels of IT management. Based in Florida, our focus is primarily on the Florida market, but we have clients and recruit candidates nationally.
